snippet.title: Space Harrier/スペースハリアー (Nec Pc-8801, 1987, Sega/Dempa Shimbunsha/Kazuhisa Ishida)
snippet.description: This is Space Harrier for Nec Pc-8801 and the graphics are way too seizure inducing that it was hurting my eyes and I could beat stage 7 and it is hard since the movement in the game is way too fast and it made my eyes hurt but once again the Music in the game is the best and I hope I can keep on playing this in the future.
